RxNorm and RxNorm Extension

Source: vignettes/rxnorm-and-rxnorm-extension.Rmd
rxnorm-and-rxnorm-extension.Rmd
library(chariotViz)
library(tidyverse)
omop_relationships <- 
  fetch_omop_relationships(
    "RxNorm",
    "RxNorm Extension",
    version_key = get_version_key())
#> ℹ Getting total concept class counts
#> ✓ Getting total concept class counts [529ms]
#> 
#> ℹ Getting total vocabulary counts
#> ✓ Getting total vocabulary counts [525ms]
#> 
omop_nodes_and_edges <- 
  create_nodes_and_edges(omop_relationships = omop_relationships)
omop_nodes_and_edges <- 
  omop_nodes_and_edges %>% 
  add_tooltip() %>%
  map_node_attributes() %>% 
  map_edge_attributes()
#> ℹ Shape from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Style from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Color from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Fillcolor from: vocabulary_id
#> ! 18 values not mapped: SPL, AMT, GGR, JMDC, KDC, Multum, VA Product, dm+d, UK Biobank, BDPM, NCCD, CVX, PPI, CIEL, Read, EDI, OPCS4, and DPD. Mapping to `other` value 'gray20'.
#> ℹ Fontcolor from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 3 constant attributes added: fontsize, width, and height.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 6 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 2 constant attributes added: fontsize and len.
omop_graph <- 
  construct_graph(omop_nodes_and_edges)
rxnorm_relationships <- omop_relationships
rxnorm_relationships@data <- 
  bind_rows(
  omop_relationships %>% 
    filter_omop_relationships(
      vocabulary_id_1 %in% c("RxNorm"),
      vocabulary_id_2 %in% c("RxNorm Extension")) %>% 
    slot(name = "data"),
    omop_relationships %>% 
    filter_omop_relationships(
      vocabulary_id_1 %in% c("RxNorm Extension"),
      vocabulary_id_2 %in% c("RxNorm")) %>%
    slot(name = "data")) %>%
  distinct() %>% 
  arrange(vocabulary_id_1, 
          vocabulary_id_2)
rxnorm_graph <- 
  create_nodes_and_edges(rxnorm_relationships) %>% 
  add_tooltip() %>% 
  map_node_attributes() %>% 
  map_edge_attributes() %>% 
  construct_graph()
#> ℹ Shape from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Style from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Color from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Fillcolor from: vocabulary_id
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Fontcolor from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 3 constant attributes added: fontsize, width, and height.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 2 constant attributes added: fontsize and len.
chariotViz(rxnorm_graph,
           force = TRUE,
           width = 2000,
           height = 2000)
#>                              ─────────────────────
#>                                n nodes   n edges

rxnorm_graph@graph$edges_df %>%

        vocabulary_id_2,
        relationship_source,
        sort = TRUE)

rxnorm_relationships <- omop_relationships
rxnorm_relationships@data <- 
  bind_rows(
  omop_relationships %>% 
    filter_omop_relationships(
      vocabulary_id_1 %in% c("RxNorm"),
      vocabulary_id_2 %in% c("RxNorm")) %>% 
    slot(name = "data")) %>%
  distinct() %>% 
  group_by(concept_class_id_1,
           standard_concept_1) %>% 
  mutate(count_1 = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(concept_class_id_2,
           standard_concept_2) %>% 
  mutate(count_2 = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  arrange(desc(count_1),
          desc(count_2)) %>% 
  select(-count_1,
         -count_2)

rxnorm_graph <- 
  create_nodes_and_edges(rxnorm_relationships) %>% 
  add_tooltip() %>% 
  map_node_attributes() %>% 
  map_edge_attributes() %>% 
  construct_graph()
#> ℹ Shape from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Style from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Color from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ Fillcolor from: vocabulary_id
#> ✓ All 1 unique value mapped.
#> ℹ Fontcolor from: standard_concept
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 3 constant attributes added: fontsize, width, and height.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 3 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ✓ All 2 unique values mapped.
#> ℹ 2 constant attributes added: fontsize and len.

           height = 2500)

rxnorm_relationships <- omop_relationships
rxnorm_relationships@data <- 
  bind_rows(
  omop_relationships %>% 
    filter_omop_relationships(
      vocabulary_id_1 %in% c("RxNorm"),
      vocabulary_id_2 %in% c("RxNorm")) %>% 
    slot(name = "data")) %>%
  distinct() %>% 
  group_by(concept_class_id_1,
           standard_concept_1) %>% 
  mutate(count_1 = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(concept_class_id_2,
           standard_concept_2) %>% 
  mutate(count_2 = n()) %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  arrange(desc(count_1),
          desc(count_2)) %>% 
  select(-count_1,
         -count_2) %>% 
  dplyr::filter(relationship_source == "RxNorm"|is.na(relationship_source))
